---
description: Guidelines for generating automated Playwright tests using Playwright MCP. Use when keywords like "generate test" mentioned.
alwaysApply: false
---
  Dynamically generates Playwright MCP UI tests.
  Parameters: searchTopic, numTests, scope.

parameters:
  searchTopic: { type: string }
  numTests: { type: int, default: 3 }

login:
  url: https://www.google.com/

prompt: |
  Use Playwright MCP.
  1. Log in at {{login.url}}.
  2. Search for {{searchTopic}}
  3. Enter the first reslt
  4. Generate {{numTests}} POM‑style tests with clear selectors and proper waits.
  5. Save to tests/ui/{{searchTopic}}_generated.spec.ts in TypeScript.